            <title>[LU-12941] Track aliveness at the peer level</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12941</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Re-introduce lp_alive. This tracks the aliveness of a peer so we can optimize for cases where all of the peer&apos;s lpni&apos;s are down. This allows us to avoid scanning all of the lpnis to determine whether the peer is reachable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
